        {
            "title": "聯準會古爾斯比稱近期通膨數據為「壞消息」,呼籲謹慎行事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/yztcdWicAvWjMjT_21H1Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_5_M_1440048359.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong> 芝加哥聯邦儲備銀行總裁奧斯坦·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"古爾斯比\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:古爾斯比;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/古爾斯比\">古爾斯比</a>於週六表示,近期通膨數據對美國央行而言是「壞消息」,顯示在降息問題上仍需保持謹慎。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據路透社首先報導,古爾斯比在接受福斯新聞《華爾街日報編輯報告》採訪時強調,聯準會需要進一步確認物價壓力正在回歸2%目標,才會放寬政策。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此番言論是在數據顯示個人消費支出(PCE)物價指數(聯準會首選指標)於3月份以3.5%的年率攀升之後發表的。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">古爾斯比強調,通膨現在甚至出現在通常不受關稅等外部衝擊影響的服務業板塊。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e1f18b28-e1e7-322a-a0c7-ed7dbd40bf3c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他指出,目前的通膨結構「看起來不妙」,特別是在油價上漲和涉及伊朗的地緣政治緊張局勢加劇現有風險的情況下。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>分歧的聯準會應對領導層過渡與政策路徑</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">古爾斯比的鷹派論調與目前正經歷數十年來最嚴重內部分歧的央行立場一致。在上週的會議上,聯準會將政策利率維持在3.5%至3.75%區間,但8比4的投票結果標誌著自1992年以來最分裂的決定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯準會的分歧源於對「前瞻性指引」的意見不一,多位官員反對暗示下一步行動可能是降息的措辭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在聯準會準備迎接領導層變動之際,這種政策不確定性隨之而來,凱文·沃什正在等待參議院確認,以接替傑羅姆·鮑威爾擔任主席。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">古爾斯比對沃什的到來表示熱情,同時歡迎鮑威爾決定留任理事會。「他一直很明智,而且很有見地,」古爾斯比談到鮑威爾時說,並補充說他對沃什將對央行發展軌跡產生的影響感到「興奮」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83%E5%8F%A4%E7%88%BE%E6%96%AF%E6%AF%94%E7%A8%B1%E8%BF%91%E6%9C%9F%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E7%82%BA-%E5%A3%9E%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E8%AC%B9%E6%85%8E%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%8B-235007049.html",
