        {
            "title": "中國發布阻斷禁令 規定不得遵守美國對中國煉化企業的制裁",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國發布阻斷禁令，要求在中國的企業不得遵守美國對5家涉伊朗石油交易中國企業實施的制裁措施，這一對抗性措施旨在減輕相關懲罰措施的影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這5家中國企業 —— 包括上月被制裁的恆力石化（大連）煉化有限公司以及其他幾家民煉化企業 —— 已面臨資產凍結和交易禁令等美國制裁措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國商務部對此採取了一項罕見舉措，發布阻斷禁令，規定不得承認、不得執行、不得遵守美國對上述5家中國企業的制裁措施。商務部在周六聲明中稱，美國的相關措施不當禁止或限制中國企業與第三國（地區）開展正常的經貿及相關活動，違反國際法和國際關係基本準則。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-adf09ce9-3905-3ca7-99d7-7027724a6b74-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「中國政府一貫反對缺乏聯合國授權和國際法依據的單邊制裁，」該部表示。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國罕見制裁中國大型煉油民企 凸顯推動伊朗重回談判桌的決心</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Beijing Tells Chinese Firms to Ignore US Sanctions on Refiners</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B8%83%E9%98%BB%E6%96%B7%E7%A6%81%E4%BB%A4-%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E9%81%B5%E5%AE%88%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%85%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%88%B6%E8%A3%81-144407458.html",
